txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Tough carapaces from the spiders to the west of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'We will find a use for these items. Thank you.'
'We can find a use for the toughened carapaces of the spiders to the west of Esteldín. Deliver them to me here.'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Tough Carapaces
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of tough carapaces to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the tough carapaces to Ferrif in Esteldín
You have accepted a task to collect tough carapaces from the spiders in the area surrounding Esteldín to the west. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: Tough carapaces from the spiders to the west of Esteldín.
